snippet.title: Announcement Trailer | Sherlock Holmes Chapter One
snippet.description:
In this story-driven detective thriller, a young Sherlock Holmes struggles to prove himself as he navigates an exotic, dangerous island in the Mediterranean to investigate the mystery of his mother’s death.

Coming to PC, Xbox One, PS4 and next gen in 2021! Wishlist now on your favorite PC platform!

Wishlist now
Steam: https://bit.ly/2X0dksX
EGS: https://bit.ly/2ZCB1t0
GOG: https://bit.ly/2WYzjR5
Consoles: Coming later!
